OL,3,CStarmer's replacement as prime
OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer's successor must
OL,8,Fimmediately slash energy bills, the
OL,9,FSNP has said.
OL,11,FThe party made the call as consumers
OL,12,Fface a 13% rise in energy bills from
OL,13,Fthe start of July ` with the average
OL,14,Fyearly bill climbing to #1,862.
OL,16,FSNP Westminster Dave Doogan warned
OL,17,FLabour against failing to keep its
OL,18,Fmanifesto pledge to reduce energy
OL,19,Fbills by #300 by 2030.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
