OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782348483
OL,3,CStarmer's replacement as prime
OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FFollowing the Prime Minister's
OL,8,Fresignation, and the strong
OL,9,Fpossibility that he will be replaced
OL,10,Fby Andy Burnham, research from the
OL,11,FHouse of Commons Library on energy
OL,12,Fprices, commissioned by the SNP, has
OL,13,Fbeen published.
OL,15,FIt shows the looming price rise will
OL,16,Fbe the sixth increase in energy bills
OL,17,Fsince Labour returned to Government in
OL,18,F2024, increasing by #294 in that time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
