FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782348483
OL,3,CStarmer's replacement as prime
OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe SNP said the analysis showed
OL,8,Fenergy had "soared" under successive
OL,9,FUK governments.
OL,11,FAccording to the Commons Library,
OL,12,Fhouseholds at the turn of the century
OL,13,Fspent an average of #11.44 a week on
OL,14,Felectricity at today's prices.
OL,16,FAt the most recent count, weekly
OL,17,Fspending on electricity had risen to
OL,18,F#21.79 per week. Weekly spending on
OL,19,Fgas has risen from #11.39 to #20.59.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
