CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782348483
OL,3,CStarmer's replacement as prime
OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FFor households reliant on heating oil
OL,8,F` about 142,000 in Scotland ` the cost
OL,9,Fof energy has risen even higher.
OL,11,FIn 1999, the typical UK mid-month
OL,12,Fprice for heating oil was 25.1 pence
OL,13,Fper litre in today's prices.
OL,15,FBy July 2024, that had risen to 62.8
OL,16,Fpence per litre and, by May 2026, it
OL,17,Fhad risen to 89.7 pence per litre ` a
OL,18,Freal terms increase of 56% since 2024
OL,19,Fand 357% since 1999.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
