OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782348483
OL,3,CStarmer's replacement as prime
OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe SNP said the UK Government's tax
OL,8,Fand energy policies were having an
OL,9,Fimpact on prices.
OL,11,FIt said the 5% VAT placed on energy
OL,12,Fadds #86 per year on average, while
OL,13,Fpolicies on standing charges have also
OL,14,Fseen costs grow in recent years.
OL,16,FMr Doogan said: "The next UK prime
OL,17,Fminister must immediately slash the
OL,18,Fcost of energy bills to avoid damaging
OL,19,Ftheir reputation by repeating another
OL,20,Fbroken Labour Party election promise.
OL,26,@xD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
