OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782348483
OL,3,CStarmer's replacement as prime
OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"From next week, energy bills will
OL,8,Fincrease to almost #600 more than the
OL,9,FLabour Party promised at the election
OL,10,F` leaving millions of households
OL,11,Fpaying through the nose in rip-off
OL,12,FBritain.
OL,14,F"The betrayal on energy bills is one
OL,15,Fof the biggest symbols of the litany
OL,16,Fof broken promises by the Labour
OL,17,FGovernment ` and reversing it is
OL,18,Fessential for any Prime Minister who
OL,19,Fwants to avoid the same fate as Keir
OL,20,FStarmer. It will be one of the first
OL,21,Fbig tests of the next prime minister.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
