OL,3,CStarmer's replacement as prime
OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"While many parts of Scotland and the
OL,8,FUK are currently enjoying sunny
OL,9,Fweather, the soaring cost of
OL,10,Felectricity will still hit families
OL,11,Fhard when it comes to powering our
OL,12,Fhomes and the energy-intensive
OL,13,Fappliances households use on a daily
OL,14,Fbasis, including showers, washing
OL,15,Fmachines, fridge freezers, TVs,
OL,16,Fcookers, and air fans."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@WO]
