OL,3,CStarmer's replacement as prime
OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Doogan said Scots would be hit
OL,8,Fhardest by energy costs with families
OL,9,Fnorth of the Border "forced to pay
OL,10,Fsome of the highest standing charges
OL,11,Fanywhere in Broken Brexit Britain".
OL,26,@qD@UOUsD@bO]
