OL,3,CStarmer's replacement as prime
OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe added: "It is a scandal that
OL,8,Ffamilies in energy-rich Scotland are
OL,9,Fbeing forced to pay sky-high energy
OL,10,Fbills by the Labour government.
OL,11,FWestminster has taken over #400
OL,12,Fbillion of Scotland's energy wealth
OL,13,Fand, instead of investing it in
OL,14,FScotland, they have closed down
OL,15,FGrangemouth and are destroying
OL,16,Fthousands of vital Scottish energy
OL,17,Fjobs in the North Sea.
OL,26,@oD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
