OL,3,CStarmer's replacement as prime
OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"It shows why it is vital that
OL,8,FScotland secures a fresh start with
OL,9,Findependence so we can use our huge
OL,10,Fenergy wealth to lower bills, create
OL,11,Fjobs and invest in our communities."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,14,FEnergy Security and Net Zero said:
OL,15,F"Tackling the affordability crisis is
OL,16,Fthe Government's number one priority.
OL,18,F"We have taken #150 of costs off
OL,19,Fenergy bills for the years ahead and
OL,20,Fextended the warm home discount to
OL,21,Faround six million households.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@dO]wD@AOUzD@AOU
