OL,4,Cminister must slash energy bills, SNP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"We are also accelerating home
OL,8,Fupgrades that will cut bills and
OL,9,Fshield families from fossil fuel
OL,10,Fshocks ` including bringing plug-in
OL,11,Fsolar to the UK."
